{"tid":1362646,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"無人機火焰噴射器　25 尺射程 + 100 秒持續噴火","createTime":"2019-07-25T02:35:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T04:16:55.000Z","uid":53524,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"df41a7ee543627bd554346908804387f0117eaed","tid":1362646,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T02:35:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=07rtBip9ixk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D07rtBip9ixk&d=%2FPdnyacYoUlJSF57jd07D7BzIjlmttHRdZ2xAWa028c%3D&h=651c4d33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=07rtBip9ixk</a><br />\n無人機近年不斷普及，引起了不少聲音，表示無人機會引發個人私隱及安全問題，不過並沒有共識，主要原因是因為無人機在不同用途上，都可以帶來好處，而現在就有最新產品推出，相信會再一次引起安全爭議，就是一台配備火焰噴射器的無人機上架，可以產生持續 100 秒的火炎發射。<br />\n<br />\n這款產品名為Throwflame TF-19 Wasp，可以是一款可以在商業重型無人機上，配備火焰噴射器，可以擊中25英尺以外的目標，油箱有 1 加侖，可以產生持續100秒的火力輸出，因此可以讓用戶無需要再背上發射器，走到目標前發射。<br />\n<br />\n公司的創辦人表示，安全是他們的首要任務，火焰噴射器不會造成傷害，可以野外 BBQ 或清除雜草等功能。Throwflame TF-19 Wasp可以安裝在大疆S1000等無人機上，需要6S 16,000mAh LiPo電池，才可以完全運作。<br />\n<br />\nThrowflame TF-19 Wasp火焰噴射器售價為1499美元，不過售價中並不包括無人機，因此需要購買全套裝備的話，需要額外2600美元購買，各位要注意啊。"},{"pid":"637d6ddba383c43a7ace39444ef885a185c7d678","tid":1362646,"uid":274725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T02:58:01.000Z","msg":"野外 BBQ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da8eda2df714008cc8c376317808459542637cdb","tid":1362646,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T03:04:39.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">727對準鄉黑：南邊圍福德堂</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i1.wp.com/tmhk.org/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/IMAGE-2019-07-22-034503.jpg?fit=1280%2C852&amp;ssl=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Ftmhk.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F